        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIG. 12. — Acteonellidae: A, Acteonella styriaca Kollmann, 1965, Turonian, Gams bei Hieflau (Austria), figure from Kollmann 1965, NHMW 1965/664/13;B, Acteonella jicarensis Sohl & Kollmann,1985,Sabana Grande Quadrangle,Puerto Rico,Late Middle Maastrichtian,NHMW 2013/0267/0002;C, Neocylindrites gosaviensis Kollmann,1967,Gams bei Hieflau (Austria),Turonian,NHMW1967/724/2; D, Trochactaeon lamarcki (Sowerby, 1831), Gams bei Hieflau (Austria), Turonian, NHMW 1836/II/18; E, F, Trochactaeon subglobosus (Münster, 1844);?Campanian, Sebes, Romania, NHMW 1967/749; E, shows the resorbed columella; F, furrows in the parietal wall might be traces of a posterior pallial cavity. Scale bars: 10 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4538519/files/figure.png" .

